return if another one was made.&amp;nbsp; It kinda sucks that we were&#xD;
forced to leave the hardcore no rules pvp server and forced onto a&#xD;
watered down lvl limit pvp server with rules.&amp;nbsp; I did not level my&#xD;
character 70 lvls and multiple aa to play that.&amp;nbsp; I leveled my&#xD;
character to play on hardcore pvp sullon zek rule set.&lt;br&gt;&#xD;
&lt;br&gt;&#xD;
