&lt;br&gt;&#xD;
And just would like to see no selos CHORUS (lvl 5 selos fine) for&#xD;
bards, and no bard divine aura if there was a no rules pvp&#xD;
server.&amp;nbsp; Otherwise bards are just WAYYY too overpowered.&amp;nbsp; At&#xD;
least this way it takes skill to shut down a raid as a bard&#xD;
trainer.&amp;nbsp; You would have to weave your songs instead of just&#xD;
playing resist songs with chorus on.&amp;nbsp; &lt;br&gt;&#xD;
&lt;br&gt;&#xD;
I really would love a new sullon zek server out.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; And just&#xD;
think about it.&amp;nbsp; No rules.&amp;nbsp; Soe would just have to put up the&#xD;
server and not even worry about it.&amp;nbsp; (though it would be nice if&#xD;
